(1329, 'Michele M.', 'michele.marinelli1977@yahoo.com', 'A new way to deliver clinical hydrotherapy', 'Hi, \r\n \r\ntwo tools, one goal: faster, safer rehab in water. \r\n \r\nThe Fitness Capsule is a sealed, single-user hydrotherapy chamber with fresh water for every session â designed for post-op and immunocompromised patients who cannot share a pool but still need full-body water therapy. \r\n \r\nThe modular rehabilitation pool handles everything else: group sessions, gait retraining, balance work, and athletic return-to-running, with a movable floor that lets therapists control load and depth in seconds. \r\n \r\nNo concrete. No construction zone. Just plug clinical hydrotherapy into your existing space and start treating patients in days, not months. \r\n \r\nSee how both systems can fit your workflow: https://shorturl.at/k1FCF', '2026-02-12 04:34:15.338859'),
