(1376, 'Wilton', 'worsnop.wilton@msn.com', 'Are you missing 20â40% of your organic traffic?', 'Hello,\r\nSaw a pattern in how your pages are ranking â and I think itâs worth 15 minutes.\r\n\r\nIn this session, I review your site and pinpoint 3 specific growth areas that could unlock an additional 20â40% organic traffic over the next 30â60 days.\r\n\r\nThis isnât a document or a template.\r\n\r\nOn a focused 15â20 min live call, I walk through:\r\nâ¢ the 3 main constraints limiting search visibility of your site\r\nâ¢ what impact adjusting them could create\r\nâ¢ a realistic traffic projection range\r\nâ¢ a simple 30-day action outline\r\n\r\nYou leave the session with:\r\nâ clarity on where visibility is being lost\r\nâ 3 priority improvements for your site\r\nâ an estimated growth range\r\nâ a practical next-step direction\r\n\r\nNo attachments. No generic slides. Just live, tailored insight.\r\n\r\nI keep this to a handful of sessions weekly to stay focused.\r\n\r\nWould it make sense to share one of the open time slots?\r\n\r\nYou can check availability here:\r\nhttps://calendly.com/seoseamarketing-agency/15min\r\n\r\nAnd if you\'re absolutely confident your organic traffic is fully optimized\r\nand thereâs no realistic room for additional growth â just reply ânoâ\r\nand I wonât follow up again.\r\n\r\nBest,\r\nLana, SEO Consultant at S&S Marketing Agency', '2026-03-10 10:13:12.325352'),
(1377, 'Theodore', 'JenniferWalshEDU@outlook.com', 'Private VPN on your own server. No subscriptions, no shared IPs.', 'A few years ago only a handful of countries blocked commercial VPNs. Today that list is much longer and growing faster than most people realize. The mechanism is always the same: the provider IP ranges are public knowledge, blocking them takes minutes, and every customer loses access instantly. If you are watching this trend and thinking your current VPN service is safe, you are probably wrong and the only question is when. A private VPN on your own VPS is not a product that can be blacklisted as a brand. Setup $40 once in crypto, after that only your regular hosting costs. I do the full installation remotely, all you need to do is give me access to your server. Message me to get it running.\r\n\r\nTelegram: @Chamerion\r\nEmail: workbench21@gmail.com', '2026-03-10 18:01:54.236294'),
